 />\nCounter <span style=\"color: red;\">Rocket, Artillery, Morter</span><br />\n火箭, 火炮同埋逼擊炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北泡2xxx-6xxx碌火炮對住首爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c06d0b674bf18ce4c21be741e3c661a406d404","tid":198608,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"預期買套作用有限嘅防禦系統<br />\n不如做好先發制人同情報工作仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8f164133445104ecd80dbace4f8503b35abe62","tid":198608,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>知唔知火箭同火炮飽受攻擊既分別</blockquote><br />\n一樣㗎囉<br />\n呢防空系統係C-RAM<br />\nCounter <span style=\"color: red;\">Rocket, Artillery, Morter</span><br />\n火箭, 火炮同埋逼擊炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北泡2xxx-6xxx碌火炮對住首爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話首爾一定唔會中彈<br />\n不過一定唔會好似主流傳媒吹得咁大<br />\n唔會好似俾人用核彈炸完咁<br />\n<br />\n南韓一套都唔買真係唔多掂<br />\n唔保護首爾都保護下啲軍事設施啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c13f4759cd93264d8046d1f5bedf0db9d8a5bf","tid":198608,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預期買套作用有限嘅防禦系統<br />\n不如做好先發制人同情報工作仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國海軍對住反艦導彈都有多層防衛啦<br />\n唔係淨係靠AEGIS<br />\n隻隻船都有部CIWS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e238d10e7727f50655702363213c6cf27463f1f6","tid":198608,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破滅魔劍</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c3a5eda22a40ee6997385e4d0c3b858d8818bb7","tid":198608,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":